    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and honest value\u2014this vehicle is a solid opportunity for the right buyer seeking dependable transportation on a budget, a work-ready spare, or a worthwhile project. It shows its age and will benefit from attention, but it presents well for its segment and offers a lot of usefulness for the money. Priced to sell with clear value in today\u2019s market.",
