    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Clean title and priced to move, this is a solid budget-friendly option for someone looking for basic, affordable transportation. It\u2019s not a perfect car, but it starts up, gets you where you need to go, and has plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great fit for a commuter, first-time driver, or someone who wants an inexpensive runaround without a lot of fuss. If you\u2019re looking for honest value and a car you can put to work right away, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
