      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly ride with plenty of usable life left and the kind of straightforward mechanical layout DIY owners appreciate. Runs, drives, and delivers dependable point-A-to-B duty, with a powertrain that feels willing and a chassis that remains serviceable. Cosmetics and overall condition reflect age and use, but for someone wanting affordable transportation, a starter project, or a practical beater with character, this one makes a compelling case. Priced to move and leaves room in the budget for freshening where you want it.",
      "price": 5950.0,
