    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with stories in its sheet metal and plenty of road still left for the right buyer. It\u2019s the kind of machine that appeals to a hands-on owner\u2014something you can tinker with, revive, or simply put to work without worrying about keeping it under a silk cover. It has a seasoned, lived-in character and the kind of presence that makes a practical project feel exciting. Whether you need an affordable set of wheels, a weekend fixer-upper, or a solid starting point for something creative, this one offers opportunity at an approachable price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical option for a buyer seeking affordable transportation, a project, or a dependable extra car. It shows its age and wear, but it offers a lot of utility for the money and is being presented with clear, honest positioning. If you want straightforward value without overpaying, this is a compelling opportunity.",
