    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest little car being sold as-is \u2014 not a showroom piece, but a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants affordable wheels, a project, or a handy spare. It\u2019s got the usual wear you\u2019d expect and could use some TLC, but for the right buyer there\u2019s still plenty of value here. If you\u2019re looking for cheap transportation without spending a fortune, this could be a great fit. Priced fairly and ready to go to its next home.",
      "price": 4900.0,
